OL,3,CGuns N' Roses' guitar hopes to fetch
OL,4,C#300,000 at music memorabilia auction
OL,6,FThe guitar used by Slash of Guns N'
OL,7,FRoses during the chart-topping rock
OL,8,Fgroup's Not In This Lifetime tour is
OL,9,Fexpected to fetch as much as #300,000
OL,10,Fwhen it is offered at auction.
OL,12,FThe photo-matched, stage-used and
OL,13,Fautographed Gibson Les Paul '59 Custom
OL,14,FShop guitar was played during the US
OL,15,Fband's 2016 tour, which saw Axl Rose,
OL,16,FSlash and Duff McKagan reunite for the
OL,17,Ffirst time since 1993.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
