PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774915371
OL,3,CGuns N' Roses' guitar hopes to fetch
OL,4,C#300,000 at music memorabilia auction
OL,6,FThe instrument, which carries an
OL,7,Festimate of #150,000 to #300,000, is
OL,8,Fdue to go under the hammer at
OL,9,FPropstore auction house in London next
OL,10,Fmonth as part of the Music Memorabilia
OL,11,FLive Auction collection.
OL,13,FA jacket worn by the late George
OL,14,FMichael during the music video for his
OL,15,F1987 hit single Faith is also up for
OL,16,Fsale, and hopes to fetch between
OL,17,F#60,000 and #120,000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774915371
OL,3,CGuns N' Roses' guitar hopes to fetch
OL,4,C#300,000 at music memorabilia auction
OL,6,FThe Grammy-winning artist, known for
OL,7,Fhits including Father Figure and One
OL,8,FMore Try, also wore the jacket onstage
OL,9,Fduring his Faith tour in 1998.
OL,11,FThe auction is taking place on April
OL,12,F30 and will also include a gold
OL,13,Fmicrophone presented to rock band
OL,14,FQueen and used by frontman Freddie
OL,15,FMercury, which expects to sell for
OL,16,F#30,000 to #60,000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
