PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774915371
OL,3,CGuns N' Roses' guitar hopes to fetch
OL,4,C#300,000 at music memorabilia auction
OL,6,FThe microphone is part of a collection
OL,7,Fbelonging to Peter Hince, the band's
OL,8,Fhead roadie and auction consignor, who
OL,9,Fsaid he has "wonderful memories"
OL,10,Fworking with the best-selling group.
OL,12,FHe added: "I'm pleased to be offering
OL,13,F(these items) through Propstore, where
OL,14,Fthey can now be shared with fans and
OL,15,Fcollectors who appreciate what they
OL,16,Frepresent in Queen's story."
