PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774915371
OL,3,CGuns N' Roses' guitar hopes to fetch
OL,4,C#300,000 at music memorabilia auction
OL,6,FAlso up for sale is an autographed
OL,7,Flarge-format promotional poster for
OL,8,FJohn Lennon and Yoko Ono's Double
OL,9,FFantasy, signed by the former Beatles
OL,10,Fsinger hours before his death in 1980,
OL,11,Faged 40.
OL,13,FThe item is expected to fetch between
OL,14,F#60,000 and #120,000 and is up for
OL,15,Fsale alongside handwritten lyrics to
OL,16,FGoodbye written by Lennon's bandmate,
OL,17,FSir Paul McCartney, which dates to
OL,18,F1969 and is expected to fetch #55,000
OL,19,Fto #110,000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
