FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774915371
OL,3,CGuns N' Roses' guitar hopes to fetch
OL,4,C#300,000 at music memorabilia auction
OL,6,FOther items up for sale include a Fred
OL,7,FPerry trench coat belonging to the
OL,8,Flate Amy Winehouse ` which has a pre-
OL,9,Fsale estimate of #4,000 to #8,000 `
OL,10,Fand an autographed jacket worn by
OL,11,Fsinger Ed Sheeran in his Shape Of You
OL,12,Fmusic video, which is expected to sell
OL,13,Ffor between #3,500 and #7,000.
OL,15,FThe event will offer more than 400
OL,16,Flots available for worldwide bidding,
OL,17,Fwith a combined pre-sale estimate of
OL,18,F#1.5 million.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
