OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774915371
OL,3,CGuns N' Roses' guitar hopes to fetch
OL,4,C#300,000 at music memorabilia auction
OL,6,FMark Hochman, Propstore music
OL,7,Fspecialist, said: "Propstore's
OL,8,Fupcoming Music Live Auction brings
OL,9,Ftogether some of the most influential
OL,10,Fnames in popular music, from legends
OL,11,Fsuch as The Beatles, Queen, George
OL,12,FMichael and Jimi Hendrix to modern
OL,13,Fglobal stars including Ed Sheeran and
OL,14,FLittle Mix.
