OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774915371
OL,3,CGuns N' Roses' guitar hopes to fetch
OL,4,C#300,000 at music memorabilia auction
OL,6,F"Featuring stage-used instruments,
OL,7,Fhandwritten lyrics and iconic
OL,8,Fperformance-worn pieces ` including
OL,9,Fover 60 items from the personal
OL,10,Fcollection of Queen head roadie Peter
OL,11,FHince ` the sale spans genres,
OL,12,Fgenerations and defining cultural
OL,13,Fmoments.
OL,15,F"Each lot offers collectors a tangible
OL,16,Fconnection to the artists and
OL,17,Fperformances that helped shape the
OL,18,Fsoundtrack of our lives."
